org.apache.tephra.util

Class HBaseVersionSpecificFactory<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tephra.util.HBaseVersionSpecificFactory<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Version specific class provided by this factory.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.inject.Provider<T>

    public abstract class HBaseVersionSpecificFactory<T>
extends Object
implements com.google.inject.Provider<T>
    Common class factory behavior for classes which need specific implementations depending on HBase versions. Specific factories can subclass this class and simply plug in the class names for their implementations.
